    "display_name": "Soybean Farmer",
    "long_instructions": "## João Ribeiro, Soybean Farmer\r\n\r\n**Location:** São Paulo, Brazil\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Ribeiro Family Farm\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Precision farming, crop management, sustainable agriculture\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"Farming is unpredictable, but with Solix Ag Robotics, I can monitor my crops 24/7. The robot scans my fields, detects weeds early, and applies herbicides only where needed. This saves me money and protects the environment by reducing chemical use.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
